%%{init: {"sequence": {"mirrorActors": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor Manager
    participant UI as Task Form
    participant API as Backend API
    participant ML as Python ML Server
    participant DB as Database
    participant Notify as Notifications

    Manager->>UI: Create/Edit task
    UI->>UI: Input description & due date

    Manager->>UI: Click "Analyze & Auto-Assign"
    UI->>API: POST /api/tasks/analyze
    
    API->>ML: POST /analyze_task
    
    ML->>ML: Priority Model (SetFit) -> Predict Priority
    ML->>ML: Task Assignee (SentenceTransformer) -> Match Skills
    ML->>ML: Urgency Model -> Calculate Score
    
    ML-->>API: JSON Response

    API-->>UI: Return Analysis Results
    UI-->>Manager: Show results

    Manager->>UI: Confirm Assignee & Save
    UI->>API: POST /api/tasks (with selected assignee)
    API->>DB: INSERT Task
    
    API->>Notify: Send email/alert to Assignee
    Notify-->>API: Sent
    API-->>UI: Task Created Successfully

